	<string name="the_long_march_intro">
In this scenario you control a (b)herd of Mammoths(/b).
You can select them, then issue various commands:
• (b)Right click(/b) on (b)terrain(/b): go there (double right click to sprint).
• (b)Right click(/b) on other (b)animals(/b): attack.
Beware of predators.
	</string>		
	
